highlights.text: “Wake Me up When September Ends” by Green Day is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Brazil, up 17 spots at #44.
“P do Pecado - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Simone Mendes has been on Viral Songs Brazil the longest, at 107 days straight.
NandaTsunami has the most spots on Viral Songs Brazil. “Pq Vc Não Me Liga?” is the highest at #6.
“Fire Fire” by Shimza, AR/CO, and Kasango is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Brazil at #89.
